{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9f96d55f5c","title":"转发山西省委关于不许在干部调动时请吃饭、照相、送礼的通知的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bd73ee43aa","index":0,"year":1955,"month":5,"day":26,"articleId":"9f96d55f5c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"915b9715c3","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"9f96d55f5c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长。"},{"id":"d00b0af77b","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"9f96d55f5c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共山西省委1955年5月22日关于不许在干部调动时请吃饭、照相、送礼给所属并报中央的通知。通知说，至今有不少单位在干部调动时，沿袭腐朽的地主、资产阶级作风，请吃饭、照相、送礼，不仅浪费了国家财产，而且对干部的思想意识有严重的腐蚀作用，在干部和群众中造成了恶劣的影响。因此，省委决定：今后无论任何机关团体、厂矿企业，在干部调动时，均不许请吃饭、照相、送礼。"}],"contents":[{"id":"07986ca843","type":"title","text":"转发山西省委关于不许在干部调动时请吃饭、照相、送礼的通知的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"9f96d55f5c"},{"id":"915b9715c3","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、邓：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"9f96d55f5c"},{"id":"d00b0af77b","type":"paragraph","text":"山西此项决定很好，可转发全党。请为中央写一指示，放在前面。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"9f96d55f5c"},{"id":"b050f080b2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"9f96d55f5c"},{"id":"fdec5587b8","type":"paragraph","text":"五月廿六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"9f96d55f5c"}],"page":{"id":"9e1f0a02be","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"9f96d55f5c","start":103,"end":103}}}},"__N_SSG":true}